  "[Resource|RESOURCE] production is a fundamental part of At the Gates.[BLANK-LINE]Initially you will simply [Harvest|HARVEST] them from [Deposits|DEPOSIT] with [Foragers|FORAGE] or buy them from the [Caravan|CARAVAN], but once your tribe is a bit more developed you'll be able to start refining raw Resources like [IRON] into other things like [TOOLS] with the help of [Professions|PROFESSION] like the [BLACKSMITH].[BLANK-LINE]Because you have a limited number of [Clans|CLAN] it's usually best to prioritize the production of one or two Resources rather than try to do everything.": "[资源|RESOURCE]生产是《At the Gates》经济的基础。[BLANK-LINE]起初，你只能让[采集者|FORAGE]从[资源点|DEPOSIT][采集|HARVEST]，或从[商队|CARAVAN]购买；部族发展后，就能借助[职业|PROFESSION]，如[BLACKSMITH]，把[IRON]等原料加工成[TOOLS]等成品。[BLANK-LINE]由于[氏族|CLAN]数量有限，通常应优先生产一两种关键[资源|RESOURCE]，不要试图什么都做。",
  "You can Study one [Tech|TECH] (usually a [Profession|PROFESSION]) at a time, and once [Learned|LEARN] you can [Train|TRAIN] your [Clans|CLAN] in it.[BLANK-LINE]The rate at which you Learn a Tech is based on its [KNOWLEDGE] cost, and how much [KNOWLEDGE] you're [Producing|PRODUCE] each turn.[BLANK-LINE]To Study more advanced Professions at least one Profession from the previous 'tier' in its [Discipline|DISCIPLINE] tree must have already been Learned.": "你一次只能[研究|STUDY]一项[技术|TECH]（通常是[职业|PROFESSION]）。[学会|LEARN]后，就能将[氏族|CLAN][训练|TRAIN]为该职业。[BLANK-LINE][学习|LEARN]速度取决于该技术的[知识|KNOWLEDGE]成本，以及你每[回合|TURN][产出|PRODUCE]多少[知识|KNOWLEDGE]。[BLANK-LINE]要研究更高级的[职业|PROFESSION]，必须先学会同一[纪律|DISCIPLINE]树上一层的至少一项职业。"
